REPLACE INTO `re_item_desc_db` VALUES ('16385', 'Headgear', '', '', 'O\'Riley\'s Green Box which can be opened to receive 1 random item.<br><span style=\'color:#ff0000\'>This box can be traded, stored, and vended. The items inside are account bound.</span><br>contains the following items:<br><br><span style=\'color:#0000ff\'>Garuda Hat</span><br>A hat which is very unique and rare, made from the feathers of a legendary bird Garuda.<br>Reduces damage from all type of monster by 5%.<br>LUK +5, HIT +10, Reduces casting delay by 5%.<br>If refined to +7 or higher, has a chance of getting Mastela Fruit when attacking monsters. Chance to drop increases by 1% for each refine level over 7.<br><span style=\'color:#ff0000\'>This item is account bound but may become tradeable in the future.</span><br><br><span style=\'color:#0000ff\'>Umbala Spirit</span><br>An accessory which is traditionally used in piercings by the Umbala tribespeople.<br>MaxHP +1%.<br>Increases the recovery rate of \'Meat\' by 25%.<br>Has a chance of dropping \'Meat\' when defeating monsters.<br><span style=\'color:#ff0000\'>This item is account bound but may become tradeable in the future.</span><br><br><span style=\'color:#0000ff\'>Grand Peco Headdress</span><br>An elaborate multi-colored headdress made from the feathers of a Grand Peco.<br>Increases attack against Demihuman and Brute type monsters 7%<br>Has a low chance of adding the curse status to your target while physically melee attacking.<br><span style=\'color:#ff0000\'>This item is account bound but may become tradeable in the future.</span><br><br><span style=\'color:#0000ff\'>Beer Hat</span><br>A mug of beer sits precariously on your head. Drinking severely impairs your ability to steer mounts or operate machinery.<br>If refined to 7 or higher, adds 100% resistance to Confusion status.<br><span style=\'color:#ff0000\'>This item is account bound but may become tradeable in the future.</span><br><br><span style=\'color:#0000ff\'>2 Battle Manual X3</span><br>This well written, detailed manual explains Extremely Efficient battle methods.<br><span style=\'color:blue\'>EXP rate increases to 300% for 30 minutes.</span>', '', '', '');
